track_notes: 06/08/13 - This is a route suggested by GM7PKT and used to activate the relevant summits 8th August 2013. Park at lay-by NN655380 (room for about three cars) and head back along the road to pick-up L/R track (alternatively you could go through gate beside lay-by and head straight up hill). Stiff pull all the way to the summit of Lawers but airy walk to SS-004 & SS-026.

track_notes: 06/08/13 - Actual Route Taken - Warning An-Stuc s NE side is treacherous especially if wet and in winter conditions. You can circumnavigate to the north of the peak and regain the bealach between Stuc & Garbh.

A linear route, easy going, easy route to follow.
